testcase.title: Cortellis-Clinical Trail reports - Biomarker-related field are not being exported correctly

steps.title: the page "Home" should be loaded on log on
I click on link 'Advanced Search' on panel 'Quick Search'
I click on tab "Clinical Trials" on 'Advanced Searched'
I select option "Biomarkers" in drop-down 'Select' in row 1 on page 'Advanced Search'
I click on image 'List' in row 1 on page 'Advanced Search'
I enter text "BRCA1" in input box on panel 'Advanced Search' pop-up
I click on button 'Look up' on pop-up 'Advanced Search'
I select term "Breast cancer type 1 susceptibility protein" from 'Select from those listed below' box on pop-up 'Advanced Search'
I click on button 'Apply' on pop-up 'Advanced Search'
I click button 'Search' on 'Advanced Search' page
I memorize the values in column "Biomarkers" for 5 reports in results page
